1d:T6d8,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Can Katie handle spring rush call volumes?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Katie handles unlimited simultaneous calls with zero wait time. During your busiest season, every caller gets answered instantly — no busy signals, no voicemail, no lost enquiries. One landscaper captured 23 enquiries in a single April Saturday using Katie."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does AI call handling work for commercial landscaping contracts?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can Katie collect garden photos from customers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Katie invites customers to send photos of their current garden to a dedicated WhatsApp number. Photos are linked to the enquiry in your dashboard, so you can prepare ideas and a rough estimate before the design visit."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What information do I get for a landscaping enquiry?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Every WhatsApp alert includes: customer name and number, postcode, garden size, property type, project type, style preference, key features requested, budget range, timeline, how they found you, and whether photos are available. Commercial enquiries also include site details."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I convert landscaping enquiries into booked jobs?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Tap 'Accept' to move to design consultation booking. Katie checks your calendar and offers available slots. For budget-conscious customers, tap 'Call Back' to discuss options. After every completed project, Claire automatically requests a Google review to build your local reputation."}}]}1e:T596,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"HowTo","name":"How to Set Up AI Call Handling for Landscapers","description":"Four-step process to get Katie answering calls for your landscaper business","totalTime":"PT30M","supply":[{"@type":"HowToSupply","name":"UK phone number or existing business line"}],"tool":[{"@type":"HowToTool","name":"Smartphone with WhatsApp"}],"step":[{"@type":"HowToStep","position":1,"name":"Customer calls about a garden project","text":"Katie answers while you're mid-plant or on a digger. She asks whether it's a redesign, patio, driveway, maintenance, or tree work"},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":2,"name":"Landscape qualification in 60 seconds","text":"Captures: garden size, property type, style preference (contemporary, traditional, low-maintenance, family-friendly), key features (patio, lawn, water feature, lighting), budget range, and start month"},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":3,"name":"Design brief to your phone","text":"WhatsApp alert: 'Garden redesign — 150m² Victorian terrace — traditional style — patio + lawn + planting — £12-18k — start May — SW6' — full context before you call back"},{"@type":"HowToStep","position":4,"name":"Accept for design visit or send portfolio","text":"Tap to accept (schedule design consultation), call back (send estimate first), or decline (sends polite message with referral). Commercial enquiries flagged for priority handling"}]}13:[[["$","script","0",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$1d"}}],["$","script","1",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$1e"}}],"$L1f","$L20","$L21"],"$L22","$L23","$L24","$L25","$L26"]
